linked to the Zapatista revolt.
</P>
<P>
   President-elect Fox had said a Salazar victory would help him
reach agreement with the Zapatistas by showing that the path to
change was through the ballot box.
</P>
<P>
   Salazar, who had been shown leading in pre-election polls, has
